product.description: The most comfortable ergonomic keyboard on the market! We just made a great deal for this Microsoft Natural ergonomic keyboard. And we know you’re going to love it. This newest addition to the world’s best selling line of ergonomic keyboards features a natural wrist alignment that will make your day!
